* Fri Jul 03 2026 RootGPT <166707820+RootGPT-YouTube@users.noreply.github.com> 0.9.4-1
- 0.9.4-beta.
- YouTube: in-app search for videos AND channels, still fully keyless (no API
  key, no login) — suggestions while typing, Everything/Videos/Channels filter,
  one-tap subscribe from channel results. The "Add channel" / "Watch a video"
  URL dialogs are replaced by the search.
